<br>
Yes, we can't solo so well (though I knock off giants now and again when I want to).  But we can do a LOT if you're creative.  However, rogues are easy to play badly and hard to play well.  A bad rogue will sit there behind the mob poking and evading constantly and not much else.  A good one will manage their agro so they can take it quickly if the cleric gets it, sneak pull, scout, CR, tank sometimes, and more.  <br>
<br>
And again, we're sexy.<br>
