<br>
Just at a guess, is Dupe a BL?  Perhaps a bit touchy over never being needed for a raid?  Well, there are classes you can't do without, classes that you need but are fairly interchangable, and classes that no one notices.  Which you play is up to you.  BL's can contribute to a raid.  You'll just have to work a bit harder finding ways to contribute and you'll never see anyone say &quot;gee, if only we had more BLs&quot; or &quot;we can't do this without a BL&quot;.<br>
<br>
OTH, if you're a BL and raiding regularly, you can rest easy knowing that people like having you around and aren't just using you because you're a critical class. <p>Mosushi, Lizard Master of the Fish<br>
